<emphasis bold="true" box="[1451,1585,2696,2730]" pageId="152" pageNumber="754">Breeding.</emphasis>
No information.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[1449,2478,2736,2770]" pageId="152" pageNumber="754" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="152.[1449,2659,2273,2888]" box="[1449,2478,2736,2770]" pageId="152" pageNumber="754">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1449,1684,2736,2770]" pageId="152" pageNumber="754">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Liberian Forest Striped Mice are terrestrial and diurnal.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
